Executive Profile
Allan J. Rimland  President, CEO, CFO, Corporate Secretary & Director, AdCare Health Systems, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships54$319,557As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Allan J. Rimland has been the President and Chief Financial Officer of AdCare Health Systems, Inc. since April 1, 2015 and has been its Chief Executive Officer since April 17, 2017. Mr. Rimland has been Corporate Secretary of AdCare Health Systems, Inc. since May 01, 2015. Mr. Rimland served as Managing Director of JMP Securities LLC. Prior to joining JMP Securities, Mr. Rimland was a Managing Director for seven years in the healthcare corporate finance group at ... Wachovia Capital Markets, where he led the healthcare services investment banking effort and executed more than 75 transactions with an aggregate value of approximately $85 billion. He is a seasoned financial executive with over 25 years of experience in investment banking and expertise within the healthcare services and related real estate industry. He served as Managing Director in the Healthcare Group, focusing on healthcare services companies from 2011 to 2015. Mr. Rimland served as a Managing Director in the healthcare corporate and investment banking group at Banc of America Securities. He previously held investment banking positions at Morgan Stanley, NatWest Markets Group and Smith Barney. Mr. Rimland has been a Director of AdCare Health Systems, Inc. since October 2015. He holds an MBA degree from the University of Chicago and a Dual Undergraduate degree in Finance and Management Policy and Computer Science Engineering from the University of Pennsylvania. He has over 20 years of healthcare services investment banking experience, including positions with leading bulge bracket and mid-sized investment banks.Read Full Background




