Allan J. Rimland



Mr. Allan J. Rimland is on the Board of Directors at AdCare Health Systems, Inc. Mr. Rimland was previously employed as a Managing Director by Healthcare Group, a Managing Director by Stephens, Inc., a Managing Director by JMP Securities LLC, and a Managing Director by Wachovia Securities, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania, an undergraduate degree from Moore School of Electrical Engineering and an MBA from The University of Chicago Booth School of Business.



